The '''Board of Intermediate and Secondary Education, Peshawar''' or '''BISE Peshawar''' is a government board for intermediate and secondary education examination located in [[Peshawar]], [[Khyber Pakhtunkhwa]], [[Pakistan]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1349929|title=Peshawar, Swat, Malakand boards declare HSSC exam results|last=Report|first=Dawn|date=2017-08-06|work=DAWN.COM|access-date=2018-06-28|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://www.urdupoint.com/en/education/board-of-intermediate-and-secondary-education-284590.html|title=Board Of Intermediate And Secondary Education Peshawar Sets Up Control Room For SSC Annual Exam - UrduPoint|work=UrduPoint|access-date=2018-06-28|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dawn.com/news/1260950|title=Schools asked not to collect fee in advance|last=Report|first=Bureau|date=2016-05-27|work=DAWN.COM|access-date=2018-06-28|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tribune.com.pk/story/1656686/1-date-announced-primary-middle-assessment-starts-govt-schools/|title=Primary, middle assessment starts in govt schools {{!}} The Express Tribune|date=2018-03-11|work=The Express Tribune|access-date=2018-06-28|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://dailytimes.com.pk/36820/kp-govt-private-schools-agree-on-5th-class-exam-by-bise/|title=KP govt, private schools agree on 5th class exam by BISE - Daily Times|date=2017-01-04|work=Daily Times|access-date=2018-06-28|language=en-US}}</ref>
== History == BISE Peshawar was established in 1961 by the [[Government of Khyber Pakhtunkhwa]]. Previously, it was conducting the examination of intermediate and secondary education for the whole [[Khyber Pakhtunkhwa]] province but later, new educational boards were established in [[Khyber Pakhtunkhwa]] by the government and now its jurisdiction is [[Peshawar Division]].<ref>http://www.bisep.com.pk/page-10016.html</ref>
== Jurisdiction == The jurisdiction of Peshawar board includes the following districts. * [[Charsadda District, Pakistan|Charsadda District]] * [[Chitral District]] * [[Peshawar District]]
